Package reportgeneration

Package to generate Extent Reports to document the Test Results

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExtentReportGenerator
    This class has method to create instance of an Extent report, configure the format of the report and to retreive the report path where it is saved.
    ExtentTestManager
    This class has methods to get the Test which is running currently.
    TestListener
    This class has methods to print logging statements for different conditions: When the execution has started, when test execution has started/failed/passed/skipped.
